            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Security Measures</h2>
                <p>We implement the following security measures:</p>
                
                <h3>Technical Safeguards</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>SSL/TLS encryption for data transmission</li>
                    <li>Secure hosting infrastructure</li>
                    <li>Regular security updates and patches</li>
                    <li>Firewall protection</li>
                    <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
                    <li>Data encryption at rest</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Organizational Safeguards</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Employee confidentiality agreements</li>
                    <li>POPIA awareness training</li>
                    <li>Access restriction based on need-to-know</li>
                    <li>Regular security audits</li>
                    <li>Incident response procedures</li>
                    <li>Vendor management and due diligence</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Your Rights as a Data Subject</h2>
                <p>Under POPIA, you have the following rights:</p>

                <h3>Right to Access</h3>
                <p>Request confirmation of what personal information we hold about you and receive a copy.</p>

                <h3>Right to Correction</h3>
                <p>Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete information.</p>

                <h3>Right to Deletion</h3>
                <p>Request deletion of your personal information (subject to legal retention requirements).</p>

                <h3>Right to Object</h3>
                <p>Object to the processing of your personal information for specific purposes.</p>

                <h3>Right to Data Portability</h3>
                <p>Receive your personal information in a structured, commonly used format.</p>

                <h3>Right to Withdraw Consent</h3>
                <p>Withdraw consent for processing at any time (where consent is the basis for processing).</p>

                <h3>Right to Lodge a Complaint</h3>
                <p>Lodge a complaint with the Information Regulator if you believe we've violated POPIA.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Data Breach Procedures</h2>
                <p>In the event of a data breach that may harm you:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>We will investigate and assess the breach within 72 hours</li>
                    <li>We will notify the Information Regulator if required</li>
                    <li>We will notify affected data subjects without undue delay</li>
                    <li>We will take steps to mitigate potential harm</li>
                    <li>We will document the breach and our response</li>
                </ol>
            </section>

