                <h3>Legal Authorities</h3>
                <p>When required by law or to protect our rights and safety.</p>

                <h3>Business Transfers</h3>
                <p>In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale (subject to continued POPIA compliance).</p>
            </section>

            <section class="legal-section">
